OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,FXi Jinping and Kim Jong Un have shared
OL,7,Ftheir intention for greater ties
OL,8,Fbetween their nations as the Chinese
OL,9,Fpresident was welcomed to North Korea
OL,10,Fin a rare state visit.
OL,12,FIn a summit between the leaders, Xi
OL,13,Fexpressed China's willingness to
OL,14,Fexpand cooperation in areas including
OL,15,Ftrade, agriculture, construction,
OL,16,Fscience and technology, according to
OL,17,FChina's Ministry of National Defence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
