OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FXi said the two countries should
OL,12,Fstrengthen strategic cooperation and
OL,13,Ffirmly safeguard their respective
OL,14,Fsovereignty and security interests,
OL,15,Fand put forward four proposals to
OL,16,Fdevelop their relationship, it said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
