PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780953074
OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,FThe Chinese leader described the two
OL,7,Fcountries as being rooted in "shared
OL,8,Fideals and beliefs" and common goals,
OL,9,Fand backed by "historical foundation,
OL,10,Fa solid political basis and strong
OL,11,Femotional bonds".
OL,13,FKim said Xi's visit "clearly
OL,14,Fdemonstrates how unbreakable" the
OL,15,FNorth Korea-China relationship is,
OL,16,Faccording to China's state broadcaster
OL,17,FCCTV.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
