PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780953074
OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,FHe also said consolidating a new era
OL,7,Fof friendship between the two nations
OL,8,Fwas the "unchanging strategic choice"
OL,9,Fof North Korea, the report said.
OL,11,FEarlier on Monday, Xi received a pomp-
OL,12,Ffilled welcome to Pyongyang to mark
OL,13,Fhis first visit to North Korea in
OL,14,Fseven years.
OL,16,FThe president and his wife Peng Liyuan
OL,17,Fwere greeted by Kim and his wife Ri
OL,18,FSol Ju, before travelling to
OL,19,FPyongyang's main square, where a
OL,20,Fmilitary honour guard and thousands of
OL,21,Fpeople staged a welcome ceremony.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
