FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780953074
OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,FChildren carried balloons, and
OL,7,Fbuildings surrounding the plaza were
OL,8,Fdraped in the two countries' flags,
OL,9,Fgiant portraits of Kim and Xi and red-
OL,10,Fand-yellow banners.
OL,12,FXi and Kim last met in Beijing in
OL,13,FSeptember, after viewing a military
OL,14,Fparade alongside Russian President
OL,15,FVladimir Putin and other foreign
OL,16,Fleaders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
