FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780953074
OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,FXi's trip comes after back-to-back
OL,7,Fsummits with US President Donald Trump
OL,8,Fand Putin in Beijing last month, and
OL,9,Fhe is expected to travel to Washington
OL,10,Flater this year.
OL,12,FChina has long been North Korea's
OL,13,Feconomic lifeline and main diplomatic
OL,14,Fbacker, but there have been questions
OL,15,Fabout their ties in recent years, with
OL,16,FKim prioritising cooperation with
OL,17,FRussia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
