FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780953074
OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,FNorth Korea has received economic and
OL,7,Fmilitary assistance from Russia in
OL,8,Freturn for supplying the nation with
OL,9,Ftroops and weapons for combat against
OL,10,FUkraine.
OL,12,FRestoring an exclusive influence over
OL,13,FNorth Korea would give Xi leverage in
OL,14,Fdealings with Trump, who has
OL,15,Frepeatedly expressed his desire to
OL,16,Frestart diplomacy with Kim, experts
OL,17,Fsay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
