FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780953074
OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,F"Implementing UN Security Council
OL,7,Fresolutions and enforcing sanctions do
OL,8,Fnot appear to be priorities for
OL,9,FChina," said Leif-Eric Easley, a
OL,10,Fprofessor at Ewha Womans University in
OL,11,FSeoul.
OL,13,FA two-way trade volume between China
OL,14,Fand North Korea last year recovered to
OL,15,Fpre-pandemic levels, and earlier this
OL,16,Fyear, the countries also resumed
OL,17,Fdirect flights and passenger trains,
OL,18,Fwhich had stalled due to Covid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
