FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780953074
OL,3,CXi Jinping vows to strengthen ties
OL,4,Cwith Kim Jong Un in North Korea visit
OL,6,FOn Monday, Xi called on both sides to
OL,7,Fleverage the opportunity of these
OL,8,Ftransport changes to increase people-
OL,9,Fto-people exchanges and foster mutual
OL,10,Finteraction, China's Ministry of
OL,11,FNational Defence said.
OL,13,FIt remains to be seen whether Kim will
OL,14,Fuse his meeting with Xi to try and
OL,15,Freengage with Washington after talks
OL,16,Fwith Trump collapsed in 2019.
OL,18,FNorth Korea has insisted the US drop
OL,19,Fits demand for the nation's
OL,20,Fdenuclearisation as a precondition for
OL,21,Ffurther negotiations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
